  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3554000/extras/8b33d97c22d4494c3915c2e88d9add04.avif?t=1744609532\" width=800 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>About this game</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you want to be a spiderbot, crawling around on ceilings and in mineshafts, drilling away to find an exit and causing blocks to fall and squish your enemies (and occasionally yourself if you are not careful?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Off course you do. So here is the game for that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig your way to victory! Upgrade your bot (perhaps with more legs or a bigger drill). Squish your enemies, and crawl away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comes with :</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mayhem</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Falling blocks that make things go 'splat'</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crawling and creeping of all sorts</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3554000/extras/a7dbdecd4719a7ba8dbdcddaa8e91c98.avif?t=1744609532\" width=800 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>A word from the developer</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for taking the time to look at this game and/or playing it. I appreciate you and hope you have fun playing this thing that leaked out of my brain space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Martijn Folmer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3554000/extras/8b33d97c22d4494c3915c2e88d9add04.avif?t=1744609532\" width=800 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>About this game</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you want to be a spiderbot, crawling around on ceilings and in mineshafts, drilling away to find an exit and causing blocks to fall and squish your enemies (and occasionally yourself if you are not careful?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Off course you do. So here is the game for that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig your way to victory! Upgrade your bot (perhaps with more legs or a bigger drill). Squish your enemies, and crawl away!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comes with :</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mayhem</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Falling blocks that make things go 'splat'</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gamepad support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crawling and creeping of all sorts</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3554000/extras/a7dbdecd4719a7ba8dbdcddaa8e91c98.avif?t=1744609532\" width=800 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>A word from the developer</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you for taking the time to look at this game and/or playing it. I appreciate you and hope you have fun playing this thing that leaked out of my brain space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Martijn Folmer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
